galculator (Algebraic and PRN calculator)

galculator is a GTK 2 / GTK 3  based calculator with ordinary
notation/reverse polish notation (RPN), a formula entry mode,
different number bases  (DEC,  HEX,  OCT,  BIN) and different
units of angular measure (DEG, RAD, GRAD).  It supports quad-
precision floating point and 112-bit binary arithmetic.

http://galculator.sourceforge.net